ilitants remaining in the city.<ref>{{cite news |title=US general says IS leaders abandoning Mosul |url=https://www.yahoo.com/news/us-general-claims-leaders-abandoning-mosul-161514664.html |accessdate=20 October 2016 |agency=AFP |date=19 October 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020174202/https://www.yahoo.com/news/us-general-claims-leaders-abandoning-mosul-161514664.html |archivedate=20 October 2016 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"theguardian1020\">{{cite news |title=Iraqi special forces launch 'large-scale' operation to retake Mosul |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/oct/20/mosul-attack-kurdish-forces-launch-large-scale-operation-against-isis-in-iraq |accessdate=20 October 2016 |work=[[The Guardian]] |date=20 October 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020174721/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/oct/20/mosul-attack-kurdish-forces-launch-large-scale-operation-against-isis-in-iraq |archivedate=20 October 2016 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n\nThe fighting intensified on 20 October.<ref name=\"cnn1020\">{{cite news |last1=Wedeman |first1=Ben |last2=Dewan |first2=Angela |last3=McKirdy |first3=Euan |title=Mosul: Most intense day of fighting since offensive began |url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/10/20/middleeast/mosul-isis-operation-iraq/ |accessdate=20 October 2016 |publisher=CNN |date=20 October 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021070924/http://www.cnn.com/2016/10/20/middleeast/mosul-isis-operation-iraq/ |archivedate=21 October 2016 |df=dmy-all}}</ref> A large convoy of [[Iraqi Special Operations Forces|Golden Division]] arrived at positions retaken by the Peshmerga forces,<ref>{{cite news |last1=Ramsay |first1=Stuart |title=Elite troops strengthen battle for Mosul |url=https://news.sky.com/story/us-trained-iraqi-special-forces-strengthen-battle-for-mosul-10623884 |accessdate=20 October 2016 |publisher=Sky News |date=20 October 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.