39760 |title=Mosul battle: Mine blast kills French and Iraqi journalists |date=2017-06-20 |publisher=BBC News|access-date=2017-06-20 |language=en-GB |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170620172352/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-40339760 |archivedate=20 June 2017 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Mosul battle: Third journalist dies after mine blast |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-40391096 |publisher=BBC News |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170624132615/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-40391096 |archivedate=24 June 2017 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><br />{{flagicon|Iraq}} 47 Iraqi journalists killed, 55 wounded (per Federation of Arab Journalists)<ref>{{cite web |title=Bodies of two journalists killed by Islamic State in south of Mosul found |url=http://www.iraqinews.com/iraq-war/bodies-two-journalists-killed-islamic-state-south-mosul-found/ |publisher=Iraq News |accessdate=20 July 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170720095036/http://www.iraqinews.com/iraq-war/bodies-two-journalists-killed-islamic-state-south-mosul-found/ |archivedate=20 July 2017 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><br />{{flagicon|United Kingdom}} 1 British journalist injured<ref>https://www.pbs.org/wgbh/frontline/article/we-experienced-chaos-joshua-baker-on-filming-battle-for-iraq/</ref><ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RtkWQofxvhg</ref><br />'''Displaced:'''<br />1,072,170 (per IOM)<ref name=\"displacement tracking\">846,252 displaced, 225,918 returnees {{cite news |title=Displacement Tracking Matrix (DTM) |url=http://iraqdtm.iom.int/EmergencyTracking.aspx |accessdate=10 July 2017 |publisher=International Organisation For Migration |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170626032316/http://iraqdtm.iom.int/EmergencyTracking.aspx |archivedate=26 June 2017 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"unhcr1109\">{{cite web |url=http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/20161106%2